snippet.title: My day in Disney Dreamlight Valley!
snippet.description:
Join us on and adventure and see what your first day in Disney Dreamlight Valley could look like! Live magically with your Disney and Pixar friends on September 6 when the game launches in Early Access.

Pre-order Disney Dreamlight Valley now: https://disneydreamlightvalley.com/getnow 
Get the free PC Avatar Designer Tool today: https://gmlft.co/avatar-designer-tool

Join the community on:

Instagram: http://instagram.com/disneydreamlightvalley 
Twitter: http://twitter.com/DisneyDLV 
Facebook: http://facebook.com/DisneyDreamlightValley 
Discord: https://discord.com/invite/disneydreamlightvalley
